name: Byte APS
overview:
Byte APS products and services offer a complete clinical solution for the creation of clear positioners. We offer Clinicians the ability to design clear positioners in partnership with us or get Byte APS to manage the whole process.

The Byte laboratory and staff are all UK based and using the latest technologies can be available for support via phone or via the web video conference facility.

For the first time it is possible for the clinician to design clear positioners within their own practice. The Byte System allows for scanning, creation of a patient’s treatment plan using the Byte Software and the production of the required treatment stages and positioners.

Byte is a branded range of products and services that offer a total solution for the creation of clear positioners. Byte offers Practices and Clinicians the ability to create clear positioners in house, in partnership with us or get Byte to manage the whole process:
